{"tid":1778051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"即使係紐約時報記者都要小心，唔好亂受訪","createTime":"2019-12-10T15:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:32:40.000Z","uid":295532,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a6fdfad1be4165aedab3585b096357a6edcb02","tid":1778051,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>好驚訝呢單野由尋晚到而家都冇人講</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom Facebook朋友post<br />\n<br />\n社運圈有地位、而打開國際戰線的朋友親自講<br />\n<br />\n「絕對不能接受呢個記者的訪問，佢置受訪者於險境都要報導的，唔會好好保護你，爆人去台灣的那單新聞是佢做的，無好好保護手足。絕對要blacklist，必須發散俾所有人知。<br />\n<br />\n我好少會去講呢啲嘢，但我親身接受過依家記者訪問已經覺得非常唔對路，大家請身邊有關連嘅朋友小心。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HefeGwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHefeGwz.jpg&h=075af85d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f29bed1ccc46b13d83aaa225ef136aca91973ec3","tid":1778051,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f4a7b21f32dbb19ee37c977066317c22e4eef86","tid":1778051,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"d347d8e3847dfdd35cc4b6e39d2a8f9920e34e40","tid":1778051,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"達哥教大家幾時講嘢講乜嘢係自己自由<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/comxukK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcomxukK.png&h=b9a14811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfc582307e08943e34c0414e9497a416a9fff527","tid":1778051,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1caa1b3b6dca8b667a47a9434f963905e5ba5292","tid":1778051,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"其實不論任何本地或國際媒體,受訪者都有責任自己保障自己唔好講太敏感嘅野,記者只能根據你講述嘅資料去出新聞"},{"pid":"7eed7c76292df64fdb6706fb9355229fcfb67ba0","tid":1778051,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38770070a82562844cb2ce7f2661fdf793d08b06","tid":1778051,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"你接受得訪問，記者一定有你嘅contact, 你要假設你嘅聯絡資料會被公開，你唔包保佢哋唔會洩漏⋯⋯"}]}